data.description: Tons of potential with this 3bed 1bath home located near the College of Idaho.  This would make a great rental or starter home.  Seller has made recent updates including paint, new cabinets and carpets throughout the bedrooms. Lots of room to park additional toys, No HOA's and the large storage shed stays with the home. Additional interior pictures to come.
